There are 3 options to buy, starting with the printed fabric pattern to the full embroidery kit stored in a cotton bag.

A 100% cotton pre-printed panel, to aid with stitching (size 9 x 9 inches or 23 x 23 cm)

Full printed instructions for the embroidery design including a stitch library.
Stitches used, stem stitch, satin stitch and french knots
All in a cellophane bag

♡ OPTION 2 - EMBROIDERY KIT
A 100% cotton pre-printed panel with the embroidery design, to aid with stitching
DMC full skeins of Stranded Cotton in 5 colours and plastic bobbins
A 6 inch wooden embroidery hoop
2 x Size 7 John James embroidery needles 
2 x needle threaders
A piece of batting to use as stabiliser for your embroidery
Full printed instructions using stitches, backstitch, stem stitch, pistil stitch, lazy daisy, woven wheels and french knots.

Please message me with your choice of background stain.
